Class TimeTrackerFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.daisy.common.priority.timetracking.TimeTrackerFactory

  • public final class TimeTrackerFactory
extends Object
    Factory of TimeTracker objects, it allows to configure the to be created object and delays its association with the executing queue.
